translations: n.标记；邮戳（indicium 的复数形式）

phrs.translation: 标记, 邮戳, 象征, 记号

sentences.sentence: Goodwill Games name, logos, and all related indicia are trademarks of Goodwill Games, Inc.
sentences.translation: 亲善比赛名字，标识语，和所有相关标记是亲善比赛公司的商标。

sentences.sentence: On the basic of this research, a reasonable design processing flowsheet was made and good ore dressing indicia was achieved.
sentences.translation: 在该研究的基础上，选矿工艺制定了合理的流程，取得了良好的选矿指标。

sentences.sentence: An electroluminescent lamp (52) is imprinted on the graphic indicia layer (56) and a membrane switch (50) is formed on the lamp.
sentences.translation: 将场致发光灯(52)压印到图形标记层(56)上，并将薄膜开关(50)形成在所述灯上。
